Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていればいいね多分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:07.40,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒だ　君と一緒で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在の鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:16.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY？ だから今を信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:21.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誇らしくなるね君の想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:27.16,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}やたらに眩しいよその笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:31.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向かいあって本心は負けないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.98,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:09.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}灑落著夢的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:15.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是找尋著喜悅的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:25.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你帶著怎樣的光芒 向著明日起航 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:37.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傾聽憧憬著未來的心跳 那是我邁向明天的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:43.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm READY! 無垠的天空湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:48.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不要忘記今天的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:54.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}約定好一起大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:58.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心靈相通的瞬間 是如此珍重的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.32,0:02:01.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop road
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:01.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\an3}想要一直在一起 同你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要有微笑就別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:07.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在一起 和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊握通向明天的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:16.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Are you READY? 所以我相信現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:21.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的思念讓我自豪無比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:27.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的笑臉是那麼的光彩奪目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:31.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直面真心就不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:34.98,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Non stop mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}急に黙り込んで　君は手を繋いだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}茜空に消えてく今日を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}見送る長いかげぼうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}放課後は永遠みたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}サヨナラをごまかしてたね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}だけど心は旅立ちの予感を知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:20.41,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}果てしない未来への
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}躊躇いを隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑む君の夢が眩しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あと少しの季節を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}惜しむようにはしゃいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}明日への帰り道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:44.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}突然沉默不語的你 靜靜地把我的手握起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:49.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}漸漸延向地平線的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.19,0:22:54.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}訴說著一天又隨著夕陽沉去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.58,0:22:59.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你說放學後的時光就像永恆一樣漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:03.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把離別的那一刻深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:13.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}但是彼此卻都深知即將各自啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:25.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}掩飾著對未知旅途的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:33.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}微笑著的你 夢想是那樣的絢麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:39.44,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}讓我們珍惜這所剩無幾的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:44.24,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}盡情歡樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:53.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}然後踏上通往明天的歸程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊  訂貨的時候搞錯了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？  藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個倒是多出來幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.84,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了算了 這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是買了Four season的最新專輯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了店舖購入特典的海報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在店裏買的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有跟Four season毫無關係動畫海報了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太震驚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明全國上下都是同樣的特典
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是這種東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也是日本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在日本國內吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說佩裏來了  可這不是美國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs15}（馬休 佩裏：日本歷史上黑船事件中的美國海軍將領  此事件就發生在夏色奇跡取景地的靜岡縣下田市）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長  訂貨的時候對方似乎和別的歌手搞混了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像剛才已經發貨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 明天下午就能到了  勞煩再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就送給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也搞地方歧視
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京不會有這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的話應該備貨很足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且經常會有活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.75,0:02:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季真幸福啊  可以盡情去看現場演出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紗季要去東京的哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說之後會告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香也想去麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不只是去玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成為偶像麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以才想去東京啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想陪在優香的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  明天還要你來陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs15}（優香  你的蛋蛋海報呢www）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯨魚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:05:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  已經沒有貼的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（對不起  今天去不了了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,355)}（怎麼了？）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(235,355)}（對不起  感冒了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子感冒了  現在正睡著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  所以才來看她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要睡一覺就能好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨你們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和大家商量太鼓祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們家是執行委員會的成員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  要扔下凜不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那麼重的病啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒也不是很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也說沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了  就由我來照顧凜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心地睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  不能和你一起去拿海報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個下次去拿就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想到一個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向神石許願治好凜的感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一個人不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  叫上夏海和紗季吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒這種小病大家一起許願的話很簡單就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又不會少塊肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不會少麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜這麼說的話  今天就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我睡一會兒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice 紗季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  我帶了慰問品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這裏讓人安心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏期講習很辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時歡迎來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問品超受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們都已經引退了 什麼事都瞎操心有點不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說還記得麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春季大賽上贏了我們的稻中的柴田水野組合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逢澤和水越
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想和那兩個人打打看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和對方的部長聯繫過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時對方提出要打練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們是在為了秋季大賽尋找調整狀態的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說實際上我們很想上去打這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是和她們說了「後輩會幫我們報仇的」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  讓我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水越  轉學以後就沒機會了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意輸贏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後你們倆就再打場比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩雖然那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是既然要打就一定要拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺野前輩她們輸掉的時候  真的很不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然憑現在的實力還很困難…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來郵件了  是優香的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也發給夏海了哦  說凜感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「有我陪著沒問題的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反而讓人更擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  就讓她們兩個獨處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  人太多也很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又看到鯨魚了嗎  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會看到鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次得感冒都會看到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭變得很暈  然後黑色的鯨就會咕嚕嚕地冒出來在我眼前游來游去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為那個我們成為了好朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  我還以為優香忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  環同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鯨在游來游去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的凜可是相當令人震驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.97,0:10:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海和紗季也還記得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個人出人意料地在這方面少根筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是代代木演唱會的藍光碟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  現在都沒還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.40,0:11:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  這場演唱會你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了十遍  秋的個人舞蹈跳得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏在安可時唱錯歌詞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(223,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有春在台階上腳滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(253,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  能注意到那一點  真不愧是凜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我稍微好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣可不行  你明明在感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看  所以就來一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然凜這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說喊Call要適可而止  但是身體不由自主地動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,335)\fs16\fsp-2}オーイング
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs13}（オーイング: 指演唱会上在衔接副歌部分的间奏时,\N粉丝们随着节奏在台下“OH！OH！”大叫的行为。\N一般常见于脑残粉很多的偶像系演唱会）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（Four season… Four season… Four season…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論看幾次都覺得好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說哪裏厲害  看  就是這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對面秋和冬也一下子做出了一樣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(215,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  做得好像一開始就準備這麼表演似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的團隊精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然就因為是她們四個人才能這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就因為是她們四個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜喜歡的是春吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是四個人都太喜歡了  所以就沒有最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為春是最關心另外三個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(243,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些大大咧咧的 但是卻最能關心另外三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像優香一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們練習舞蹈時  你都是練夏的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(393,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做冬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Fuyumi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我做秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(340,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了一身汗感覺舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為夏一直都看著春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(302,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Chinatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(415,335)\fs16\fsp-1}Miharu
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是在說她們的站位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們經常那樣站位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天盡興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是有生以來最開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（對不起  今天我去不了了）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  優香  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像優香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是什麼可笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是這麼說的  但是她的嗓子都啞了  聽上去很痛苦的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明俗話說笨蛋是不會得感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想去探病  結果她說「快好的時候是最關鍵的時候  一定不要過來」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊  因為探病而感冒再傳回給你就太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子也一天就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天接下來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  凜有什麼想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去卡拉OK嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  快來來來來  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天沒什麼狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為優香不在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在的話就會變得很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為四個人一直都在一起  所以不曾意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少一個人就會變得這麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我要去別的地方  就在這裏分開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  之前的海報送過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君  把那張海報拿給她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  還有一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個人買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來確認一下海報是否送到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（特典海報送來了哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你病好了  一起去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個暫時是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是謝絕會面狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會轉告她說你們來過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣看來會拖很久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不回我郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我四天沒和優香見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  這種事已經幾年沒發生過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她在就會引起各種騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在心裏埋怨「都是這傢伙」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其實也是她非常努力地在為我們著想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了她我們才能和好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小學四年級時轉校過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始被大家覺得是有點奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上是有分不清夢和現實的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鯨在游來游去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環同學是騙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子環 騙子環…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊  鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木也是騙子的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  男生們太吵了 沒法學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把她送到保健室去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我優香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫我凜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的看到了吧  鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是相信你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有一起看到的那一天就好了  那個鯨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  環同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我們一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為那件事我們成了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聊了之後發現大家都是Four season的歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時很流行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們四個人還在優香的家裏練習舞蹈動作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後四個人就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格雖然很不同  但是四個人在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還覺得只要我們四個人在一起就沒有做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Four season一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到紗季去東京那天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要四個人更多地在一起  哪怕只多一天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.81,0:19:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是優香推薦的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香也一定是這樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜託你們一件事  一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向神石許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望優香的感冒能快點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感冒拖一天就少一天和她在一起的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能答應我一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不要告訴優香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她也沒什麼吧  為什麼不告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我得感冒的時候  我要優香別去向神石許願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說這樣做太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  絕對不能想奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在天上飛什麼的  想黏在一起什麼的  想交換身體什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種絕對不能想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海  這麼說出來就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  我們再四個人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你們想要祈求希望我的感冒快點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很感激  但是太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說我也已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  但是你姐姐說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了就是她說「傳給客人就不好了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就把我關在房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒得無聊  於是我就打手機遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果她說「不睡覺可不行」於是把我的手機沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒法回郵件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你還真能想到我們在這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她告訴我你們來過了  所以我就想你們應該會在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優香  優香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是制止了你們真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們許願的話一定又會發生不得了的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能像Four season那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.84,0:22:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都看見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜的感冒已經好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  徹底地完全康復了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.08,0:24:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為是夏天就掉以輕心的話  又會得的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出回來後要漱口洗手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒的病毒不光是冬季…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.26,0:24:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.43,0:24:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有睡眠不足也是禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想調理身體基本上也要靠睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急速地…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那裏有個最好休息一下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.57,0:24:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集  夏色奇跡  第六話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海的雙打
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.04,0:24:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是家務又是社團活動又是作業
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海有好好睡覺嗎
